item.description:
@Jei_Jei_KK wrote:

I shouldn’t have sended auto-talker to my cousin. He got 3 black marks and 3 day temp ban for his member 93 main. Anyways, when i saw what kind of messages he typed, no wonder he got them. Extremely high speed repeating “Green:Selling something 434k______name here____!!!”
Just don’t make it type it like every second. Human-like. Just like kingoftptw.

[offtopic] I’m now back. I should be more active, at least when i finish training my main & selling it… Btw, I’ve not seen Ron posting? What’s happening? Also, new ranks, some quiz, 30k more members, Un-Named as mod…[/offtopic]
